high_descs: turn to the left and move forward towards the window, at the window turn to the left and move forward to the left side of the sofa
pick up the striped pillow that is on the sofa
turn around and move to the black table that is to the right of the fire place
turn on the lamp on the right side of the table
anns.task_desc: examine the pillow by the light of the lamp on the black table

high_descs: Turn to your left and go past the red chair, then go to the front of the red chair and turn to your left again and go to the left end of the couch across from you.
Pick up the throw pillow on the left side of the couch.
Turn around and go to the black end table to the right of the fireplace.
Turn on the lamp on the table.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the living room lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and go right and then left and then left again to face the red couch with the striped pillow.
Pick the pillow up from the couch.
Turn around and cross the room to face the black table with the lamp on it.
Turn the lamp on the black table on.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a pillow and turn a lamp on.
